# Web screenshots referenced from README.md — kept under the same
# numbering scheme used by scripts/capture-screenshots.mjs so changes
# to that script flow through to the bundled .vsix automatically.
# Note: the hero is an animated .gif; we also ship the .png poster for
# Marketplace renderers that fall back to first-frame. The .webm source
# stays out of the bundle (large + no Marketplace renderer reads it).
!media/screenshots-web/01-hero.gif
